    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds good in theory but it feels like a bit of a gamble. like, if i have to raise my prices to cover the payroll, wont my customers just stop coming? it feels like the \"positive feedback loop\" people talk about might just be a way to ignore the actual risk of businesses closing down. what do you think, is it actually a net benefit for a place like this?",
